    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Brave Escape》是一款极具挑战性的双人合作平台游戏，两名玩家必须携手合作，在充满危险的关卡中逃出生天。自由扮演柯林和弗洛伊德，踏上一场勇敢无畏的冒险，每一次迈步、跳跃和攀爬都需要精确配合。收集道具，揭开隐藏的秘密，与伙伴一同踏上这场难忘的旅程，体验《Brave Escape》的刺激与乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有特殊能力——弗洛伊德的助推机制与柯林的攀爬绳索都是应对洞穴地形的关键工具，精准配合与解谜能力将是你们成功的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/a260799ab6d1892fa9ddd1b6fbf6c41d.poster.avif?t=1758830837\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/a260799ab6d1892fa9ddd1b6fbf6c41d.webm?t=1758830837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/a260799ab6d1892fa9ddd1b6fbf6c41d.mp4?t=1758830837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >趁手工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于你们所处的地点，弗洛伊德将装备一件特殊装置，为你们的冒险增添胜算。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冰川瀑布：风力枪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荧光深渊：手电筒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巨蛇幽穴：抓钩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摩艾密室：冷冻枪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雷霆裂谷：磁力枪</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/02098ed3e476ff70adfe7ae72551c420.poster.avif?t=1758830837\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/02098ed3e476ff70adfe7ae72551c420.webm?t=1758830837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/02098ed3e476ff70adfe7ae72551c420.mp4?t=1758830837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单模式提供更友好的游戏体验，减少尖刺挑战，并放宽判定时间。非常适合不太熟悉精准平台游戏的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras/ba965bd2fbf48932f596500801758654.avif?t=1758830837\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354260/extras_big/ba965bd2fbf48932f596500801758654.avif?t=1758830837 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开始冒险之旅吧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备吧！现在就将《Brave Escape》加入愿望单，抢先踏上这场史诗之旅！</p>",
